<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lizhehan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3574696-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lizhehan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">伪君子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-03-17"
      class="main-meta">2009-03-17 22:56:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1889599_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  考研前能读到这本书的话，估计哲学史还能多考几分。从这本书能读出来，国外的很多学者写哲学史是从Homer和Hesiod开始写的，而不是从Thales开始写的，这样就可以把诗歌等其他前哲学的思想形态和哲学联系起来。

